There will never be enough words in any language to accurately convey how I feel about you.  The best that I have found is:

I LOVE YOU

And those words do not seem like enough.  You are and always will be my everything.  It has and will always be you, only ever you.  I have always been connected to you and you have always found me. 

Bilal, you are my husband and I love you with every ounce of my being.
